quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  16,35,"Sano aŵala ŵawanganyisye (Allah ni isanamu) akutiji: “Allah angasache, nga nganitugalagatila uwwe namuno achatati ŵetu chinepe changaŵaga Jwalakwe, soni nga nganituchitenda chindu chilichose kuŵa cha haraam mwangali (lilamusi lya) Jwalakwe.” Mwele ni muŵatendele aŵala ŵapaujo pao. Ana nambi kwa Achimitenga kwana masengo gane gangaŵaga kulungusya utenga mwakupikanika"
  16,36,"Soni chisimu chene twatumisye ku nkutula uliose Ntenga (juŵausalilaga) kuti: “Mun’galagatilani Allah ni kuŵambalana najo shetani.” Basi ŵane mwa ŵanganyao pana ŵaŵajongwele Allah, ni pana ŵane mwa ŵanganyao ŵakwasimichiche pa ŵanganyao kusokonechela. Basi jendagani pa chilambo kupita nchilola mujaŵelele mbesi ja akukanila"
  16,37,"Naga nkusachilila nnope yakwajongola ŵanganyao (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ), basi (manyililani yanti): Chisimu Allah jwangan’jongola jwannechelele kusokonechela, soni nganakola ŵanganyao akwakamuchisya"
  16,38,"Ni akunnumbilaga Allah kulumbila kwao kwamachili, kuti Allah ngasiŵajimusya ŵandu ŵaakuwa. Yakuona (tachajimusya, achi ni) chilanga chaalikanganiche Nsyene mwakuonaonape, nambo ŵandu ŵajinji ngakumanyilila"
  16,39,"(Tachajimusya) kuti ŵalondechesye ayila yaakutindana pa yalakweyo, ni kuti amanyilile aŵala ŵaŵakanile kuti ŵanganyao ŵaliji ŵaunami"
  16,40,"Chisimu liloŵe Lyetu pa chindu chilichose pati tuchisachile (kuti chipatikane), tugambaga kuchisalila kuti: “Chiŵe.” Basi ni chikisaŵaga"
  16,41,"Sano aŵala ŵaasamile (nsimangwao) ligongo lya Allah panyuma pakutendeledwa lupuso, chisimu chitwatamiche pa duniya mwa umbone, soni malipilo ga ku Akhera (gagakwajembecheya) ni gagali gekulungwa nnope ingaŵe ŵamanyililaga (ŵakusakalaŵa)"
  16,42,(Ŵatakaipate yalakweyi ni) aŵala ŵaŵapilile ni kuŵa ali nkwegamila kwa M’mbuje gwaope